GDK-PIXBUF-PIXDATA

NAME

gdk-pixbuf-pixdata - GDK Pixbuf library

SYNOPSIS

gdk-pixbuf-pixdata [options] [input-file] [output-file]

DESCRIPTION

-h, --help

show this help message

-v, --version

print version information

--g-fatal-warnings

make warnings fatal (abort)
